{"timestamp": "2025-12-06 13:34:53.373002", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission details\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): switch_1\n- Root cause(s): p4_table_entry_missing\n\nRationale\n- switch_1’s MyIngress.ipv4_lpm entries were cleared by a control-plane action (bm_mt_clear_entries), and the default action was set to drop. This resulted in LPM misses and drops for all IPv4 traffic, breaking end-to-end reachability. switch_2 is forwarding correctly; hosts and links are healthy.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1895, "output_tokens": 106, "total_tokens": 2001, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1792}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
